Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:14.87,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,The tune that plays when my loneliness \Nand the pedal are stepped on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:20.42,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Tracks down my cheeks over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:24.09,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,The pounding of my loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:28.17,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Is joined by the rhythm of the snare drum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:31.26,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,To create a solid pulse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:33.80,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Someone, please remove \Nthe distortion on my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.77,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,And take a look inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:40.77,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Nobody can get inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.27,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,But it's the kind of night \Nwhen I hope someone will
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.78,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Distortion it's Motion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:50.20,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Once it starts, there's no stopping it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:54.41,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Limits can be overwritten with experience
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:55.79,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:57.83,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Distortion is always like that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:02.29,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,My heart takes off, outpacing my left brain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:03.92,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Toward where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:06.55,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,An escort to the next note
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:09.26,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Distortion on my day-to-day anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:12.13,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,The chord I play when I'm alone at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:13.59,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Is it the same for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.18,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,I spent all those days chasing my ideal image
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:20.35,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,Play an F chord with distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:24.36,CR_DefaultItalics,ED,0,0,0,,So loud that the needle swings off the scale
